1
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:12,960
I was bold enough

2
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:14,480
to use the gold inlay method

3
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,960
to connect the broken parts,

4
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:18,080
for the good luck of gold inlaid with jade.

5
00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:19,410
Please take a look, sir.

6
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,040
Forgive me, sir.

7
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:24,080
I tried to repair it,

8
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,560
but the making of this bracelet

9
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:27,640
is different from other amber.

10
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:29,740
The color is also extremely special.

11
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:32,619
Even if the broken parts are barely glued together,

12
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:33,800
these red cracks

13
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:35,120
cannot be replicated.

14
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:36,680
This gold inlay method,

15
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:37,560
though tacky,

16
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:39,360
is the only way to ensure

17
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:40,800
the original appearance of the bracelet.

18
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:41,320
Get out.

19
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:45,960
Know what to say

20
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:47,320
and what not to say.

21
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:48,720
Don't worry, sir.

22
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:51,080
I have never seen this amber bracelet.

23
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,370
Go find another.

24
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:01,760
He is already

25
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:04,019
the best bracelet craftsman in Kuizhou.

26
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:06,740
Who are you?

27
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,600
Let me try.

28
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:26,480
I can repair this bracelet.

29
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:29,280
Even the best craftsmen in Kuizhou can't do it.

30
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,480
Can you do it, my lady?

31
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,120
You can't blame them.

32
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,600
Their skills of inlaying gold and jade are excellent,

33
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,000
but this seeped-in color

34
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:39,580
is the specialty of our Yanzhi Pavilion.

35
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,360
You know seeped-in color?

36
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,280
Among

37
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,640
the rouge and lip balm

38
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,000
mixed by my cousin,

39
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:48,240
I've seen

40
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,080
dozens of shades of red,

41
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,080
if not a hundred.

42
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,880
I've seen this red color.

43
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,039
I can mix it.

44
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,080
Besides,

45
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,160
sir,

46
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:04,360
aren't you afraid that others will know

47
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,690
that you are repairing this bracelet?

48
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,639
You have something on me,

49
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,680
so I

50
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,760
will definitely keep my mouth shut.

51
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,720
Wouldn't that make me more useful

52
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,930
than those craftsmen outside?

53
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,960
If you can't restore

54
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,300
the original color of this bracelet,

55
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,160
you'll be whipped twenty times.

56
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,000
If you ruin this bracelet...

57
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,210
My life is yours.

58
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,640
But if I fix it...

59
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,680
Qionghua

60
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,530
is yours.

61
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,240
Okay.

62
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,040
It's a deal.

63
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,000
Without further ado,

64
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,900
let's go to the back mountain now.

65
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:57,680
These flowers have been in the sun long enough.

66
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,320
They have the least moisture right now.

67
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,600
It's the best time to extract the color.

68
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,360
Your injury...

69
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,040
I'm fine.

70
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,440
Wait a minute.

71
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,680
Keep this batch of juice for now.

72
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,040
Usually, it's discarded after squeezing twice.

73
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,079
But no one knows

74
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:59,370
that the color from the third squeeze is the deepest.

75
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,480
He eats nothing.

76
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,240
He only drinks a little sweet water every day.

77
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,960
Mrs. Fang is really devoted

78
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,370
to the master's matter.

79
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,010
Take good care of it.

80
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:47,290
Yes, sir.

81
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,320
This flower

82
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,000
has been out of the soil for two days,

83
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,320
and its roots are burned.

84
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,680
It really

85
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,680
can't be saved.

86
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:59,170
My mother planted Qionghua for many years

87
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,210
and is quite experienced in it.

88
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,760
Even her method doesn't work?

89
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,800
Unless it's

90
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,080
a miracle by the gods.

91
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,320
Never mind.

92
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,090
It's the will of heaven.

93
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,960
What about Lady Fang?

94
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:25,940
The time to go to the black market is tomorrow night.

95
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,760
Once I get the Qionghua seeds

96
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,440
and truly grow them,

97
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,980
she will definitely have a share.

98
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,960
I don't want to be a person

99
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,560
who breaks his promises.

100
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,000
Young Master, do you really believe

101
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,040
that Fang Qingcheng asked the lady to get the Qionghua?

102
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:42,159
What is the difference between believing and not believing?

103
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:43,600
Now this Qionghua

104
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,280
and Fang Zhuozhuo are the only two baits that can draw out

105
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,680
Fang Qingcheng.

106
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,400
Even if it's a trap,

107
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,650
I have to step in and see.

108
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:54,140
The Master ordered

109
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,120
that when he is not here,

110
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,760
no one is allowed near the study.

111
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,760
You really can't go in.

112
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,680
My lady.

113
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,560
My lady.

114
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,560
My lady.

115
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,760
You really can't go in.

116
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,720
My lady.

117
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,880
Please don't make it difficult for me.

118
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,140
You really can't go in.

119
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,640
My head hurts so much.

120
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,200
Well...

121
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,260
It hurts terribly.

122
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,720
My lady.

123
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,560
Somebody, come!

124
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,280
Oh, you Chu Shengyi.

125
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:33,680
I spent three days fixing the bracelet for you,

126
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,880
but you actually went back on your word.

127
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,020
Not letting me near the study.

128
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,480
Could it be

129
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,600
that Qionghua is still hidden here?

130
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:01,440
Playing the lute at night in the Han Palace spring.

131
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:07,360
Under a cold moon and tent with snow as a neighbor.

132
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,520
The snowy night outside the Great Wall is windy and cold.

133
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,880
How could Zhaojun still have the mood

134
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,540
and strength to play the lute?

135
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,080
Lute at night,

136
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,160
Han Palace spring.

137
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,160
That's right.

138
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:03,720
The person in this painting looks so much like Qingcheng.

139
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,720
The word 'Xinxin'

140
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:10,500
seems to have been touched so much that it faded.

141
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:14,000
The person in the painting must have 'Xin' in her name.

142
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,840
So she is the owner of this bracelet.

143
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,560
I know.

144
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:30,570
Husband, do you recognize this painting?

145
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:32,420
You went into the secret room?

146
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,480
You went back on your word,

147
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,520
so I had to find something against you

148
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,960
to make you keep your promise.

149
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,600
But it's a good thing I went in.

150
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,920
It solved the doubt in my mind.

151
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,000
It turns out

152
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,200
Qingcheng is just a substitute for the person in this painting.

153
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,040
This girl named Xinxin

154
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:53,640
is the one you truly want to marry, right?

155
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,600
How did you crack the poetry code?

156
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,640
Your mechanism

157
00:09:57,640 --> 00:10:01,700
is not even as delicate as a three-year-old child's nine-linked puzzle.

158
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,200
Give me the Qionghua.

159
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:03,880
Otherwise,

160
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,580
I won't even let you keep this little memory.

161
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:18,920
Xin'er.

162
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,680
Xin'er.

163
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,200
His leg.

164
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,880
Oh no.

165
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:41,600
Zi'er.

166
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,320
Zi'er.

167
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:46,560
Zi'er.

168
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,080
Hurry.

169
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,360
Young Master.

170
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:57,010
The Qionghua you wanted

171
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,400
has withered.

